<br>
&quot;Well, let's set up camp. Tomorrow you will claim this land before all gods, ancestors, and souls.&quot;<br>
<br>
Yakut walked past Amarice and began unrolling her bedroll, leaving Amarice to a few moments of quiet comtemplation. There was more to being Queen than powering over land and a tribe...Amarice had to realiz this on her own.<br>
<br>
After she had set up her bedroll, she decided a fire was needed. Her emerald occulars landed on Amarice.<br>
<br>
&quot;Need to start a fire, You want t go wood hunting or should I?&quot;, she smirked. Yakut didn't care either way, she was just happy to help Amarice on her path as a Queen of the Amazons. <p>§-:¦:-§ Yakut §-:¦:-§<br>
