<br>
When Yakut asked for her to find some wood for their fire place Amarice snapped back into reality and turned her head towards the Shamaness.  &quot;I'll go get some wood sense your back goes out more than you do!&quot;  and with that Amarice headed up shore and to the forest with a smirk playing her lips.<br>
<br>
