<br>
The Shamaness moved to her saddle bag and took out her cantine, she sucked a gulp into her mouth and sprayed the fire, flames crawled to Amarice encircling her but never touching her. They slithered back into the fire, nd Yakut took a seat across from Amarice.<br>
<br>
&quot;Hot enough for ya?&quot; <p>§-:¦:-§ Yakut §-:¦:-§<br>
