&quot;Well, I am seeing a vision...&quot; Amarice bring her hand to her head, touching her temple with two fingers.  &quot;I see it now....You're cooking me FOOD!&quot;  Amarice begins to laugh mockingly at Yakut.<br>
<br>
&quot;What?  I'm hungry!...&quot; <p>Ø×××|¯A_m¯a_r¯i_c¯e_&gt;</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#0000FF><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showUserPublicProfile?gid=amazonqueenyakut>Amazon Queen Yakut </A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_fire.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Amazon Queen of Tanis River Valley</span><br>  Posts: 253<br> <font color=#00FFFF>(12/8/02 9:45 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm59.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2.topic&index=15>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.hometown.aol.com/amznqyakut1/images/yakut3.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> You want food?</span><hr size=1> Yakut growled, and took some sand in her hand. She thrust her arm out spraying the sand all over Amarice. The Shamaness laughed, she was playing of course.<br>
<br>
&quot;I'll fix you some food, but only because your Queen here...&quot;<br>
<br>
Yakut got up and began looking through her saddle bags for food. She took out a bottle of red wyne, bread, a small container of pasta and some olive oil. She had gotten in her shipment from a place called Florence in the Roman empire. They made food to die for!<br>
<br>
The Shamaness quietly warmed up the pasta and served all the food up on two plates. She handed Amarice hers and some utensils before digging into her own plate. After swallowing her first bite she looked up at Amarice.<br>
<br>
&quot;How do you like pasta?&quot; <p>§-:¦:-§ Yakut §-:¦:-§<br>
