<br>
Using the utensil provided by Yakut, Amarice took the first bite of this &quot;pasta&quot;.  She then felt as if ecstacy had been let free in her mouth, she just melted with it's wonderful taste.  Amarice moved her occulars down to glance at the plate and noticed that she was going to want more afterwords.  With a quick swallow of the food she replyed, &quot;Yakut, this is amazing!  I want this food shipped regularly when my tribe gets up and going.  I was a tavern that sells just this type of food.  ...Oh Goddess!  This is amazing.&quot; <p>Ø×××|¯A_m¯a_r¯i_c¯e_&gt;</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#0000FF><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showUserPublicProfile?gid=amazonqueenyakut>Amazon Queen Yakut </A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_fire.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Amazon Queen of Tanis River Valley</span><br>  Posts: 261<br> <font color=#00FFFF>(12/17/02 10:49 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm59.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2.topic&index=17>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.hometown.aol.com/amznqyakut1/images/yakut3.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Romans</span><hr size=1> Yakut smiled, and hesitated a moment.<br>
